  <brief_title>Study Evaluating Emergency-use Tigecycline in Subjects With Resistant Pathogens.</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-label, Noncomparative, Multi-center, Emergency Use Protocol Administering Tigecycline for the Treatment of Subjects With Infections Due to Resistant Pathogens.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
